The paper presents a foraging algorithm that uses a specific mathematical ratio (Golden Ratio) to choose search direction, which suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multi-agent systems (cs.MA). The algorithm's efficiency is also discussed, which could fall under the categories of social and information networks (cs.SI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and machine learning (cs.LG).
